flowchart LR
    TC[测试控制器<br/>Test Controller]
    DS[数据准备器<br/>Data Seeder]
    LG1[负载发生器 AZ-A]
    LG2[负载发生器 AZ-B]
    LG3[负载发生器 AZ-C]
    FI[故障注入器<br/>Fault Injector]
    GW[API Gateway]
    APP[Go 秒杀接入服务]
    R[(Redis Cluster)]
    MQ[(RocketMQ)]
    CON[Go 订单消费者]
    PG[(PostgreSQL Primary)]
    OBS[Metrics / Logs / Trace]
    VA[正确性验证器<br/>Invariant Validator]
    RS[(测试结果库)]

    TC --> DS
    TC --> LG1
    TC --> LG2
    TC --> LG3
    TC --> FI

    LG1 --> GW
    LG2 --> GW
    LG3 --> GW

    GW --> APP
    APP --> R
    APP --> MQ
    MQ --> CON
    CON --> PG
    CON --> R

    FI -.故障注入.-> APP
    FI -.故障注入.-> R
    FI -.故障注入.-> MQ
    FI -.故障注入.-> PG

    GW --> OBS
    APP --> OBS
    R --> OBS
    MQ --> OBS
    CON --> OBS
    PG --> OBS
    LG1 --> OBS
    LG2 --> OBS
    LG3 --> OBS

    VA --> R
    VA --> PG
    VA --> OBS
    VA --> RS
    TC --> RS
